NoHeal v1.0
by mstiles92

This plugin simply blocks players from regenerating health due to eating food, having a full hunger bar, or potion effects.

Commands:
/noheal [enable|disable|toggle]: Displays or changes the state of the plugin's effect.

Permissions:
noheal.bypass: Allows the player to heal like normal.
noheal.toggle: Allows the player to toggle the effect on/off for the entire server.

Originally requested at http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/complete-hunger-doesnt-heal-hp.88798/